      <a href="/pages/help/privacy_policy" rel="external">Privacy Policy</a> |
      <a href="/pages/system/credits" rel="external">Credits</a><br/>
      Powered by <a href="http://beonebody.org" rel="external">OneBody</a> |
      <a href="?iphone=false" rel="external">Full Site</a>
